[
    {
        "text": "Hi, there.",
        "start": 0.269,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "Welcome back to engVid.",
        "start": 1.269,
        "duration": 2.001
    },
    {
        "text": "Today's lesson is a conversational English\none.",
        "start": 3.27,
        "duration": 3.08
    },
    {
        "text": "We are looking at vocabulary to do with secrets-sharing\nsecrets, maybe hearing a secret-so that you",
        "start": 6.35,
        "duration": 6.92
    },
    {
        "text": "understand what the other person is saying.",
        "start": 13.27,
        "duration": 3.25
    },
    {
        "text": "I'm not saying that sharing secrets is a brilliant\nthing that you need to be doing, but it's",
        "start": 16.52,
        "duration": 5.92
    },
    {
        "text": "still worth building your vocabulary, so stay\ntuned and let's listen.",
        "start": 22.44,
        "duration": 4.62
    },
    {
        "text": "First phrase: \"I've heard...\"",
        "start": 27.06,
        "duration": 3.639
    },
    {
        "text": "Obviously we have the abbreviation for \"I\nhave heard\".",
        "start": 30.699,
        "duration": 4.471
    },
    {
        "text": "\"I've heard that Lionel called Cristiano bigheaded.",
        "start": 35.17,
        "duration": 6.39
    },
    {
        "text": "Would you believe it?",
        "start": 41.56,
        "duration": 1.97
    },
    {
        "text": "I've heard that...\"",
        "start": 43.53,
        "duration": 2.459
    },
    {
        "text": "This is our introduction, then we have the\nsecret following after.",
        "start": 45.989,
        "duration": 4.791
    },
    {
        "text": "Or, if you wanted to ask it as a question:\n\"Have you heard that...?\" then put your secret.",
        "start": 50.78,
        "duration": 8.26
    },
    {
        "text": "\"Have you heard that Lionel called Cristiano\negocentric?\"",
        "start": 59.04,
        "duration": 5.92
    },
    {
        "text": "Another way of saying: \"They say...\"; \"They\"\nmeaning sort of an unquantified amount of",
        "start": 64.96,
        "duration": 6.949
    },
    {
        "text": "people.",
        "start": 71.909,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "\"They\", whoever they are.",
        "start": 72.909,
        "duration": 1.901
    },
    {
        "text": "\"They say that Lionel said this.",
        "start": 74.81,
        "duration": 4.43
    },
    {
        "text": "They say that...\"",
        "start": 79.24,
        "duration": 3.93
    },
    {
        "text": "It's quite a good way of putting blame on\nother people, rather than saying that it's",
        "start": 83.17,
        "duration": 3.799
    },
    {
        "text": "actually you saying it.",
        "start": 86.969,
        "duration": 2.241
    },
    {
        "text": "\"Just between you and me...\"",
        "start": 89.21,
        "duration": 4.179
    },
    {
        "text": "What you're doing with this phrase is setting\nup a kind of a secret relationship.",
        "start": 93.389,
        "duration": 3.87
    },
    {
        "text": "\"Just between you and me...\"",
        "start": 97.259,
        "duration": 2.121
    },
    {
        "text": "It kind of invites the other person to lean\nin a little bit closer so that they're really",
        "start": 99.38,
        "duration": 4.289
    },
    {
        "text": "listening, and no one else can hear this secret.",
        "start": 103.669,
        "duration": 3.41
    },
    {
        "text": "\"Just between\", okay?",
        "start": 107.079,
        "duration": 1.75
    },
    {
        "text": "So, we don't want anyone else to hear.",
        "start": 108.829,
        "duration": 2.96
    },
    {
        "text": "\"Just between you and me...\"",
        "start": 111.789,
        "duration": 2.72
    },
    {
        "text": "\"I heard it on the grapevine...\"",
        "start": 114.509,
        "duration": 2.77
    },
    {
        "text": "I'm sure you've all heard that classic song,\nbut we can actually use that as a conversational",
        "start": 117.279,
        "duration": 5.61
    },
    {
        "text": "phrase.",
        "start": 122.889,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "\"I heard on the grapevine that...\"",
        "start": 123.889,
        "duration": 3.04
    },
    {
        "text": "The \"grapevine\" is just this unknown place\nwhere we hear secrets; rumours.",
        "start": 126.929,
        "duration": 6.541
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 133.47,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "\"Rumour\", something that is not fact; it's\nan idea that something might be.",
        "start": 134.47,
        "duration": 5.85
    },
    {
        "text": "Let's just write that down.",
        "start": 140.32,
        "duration": 2.69
    },
    {
        "text": "So, we'll put \"rumour\" in.",
        "start": 143.01,
        "duration": 4.42
    },
    {
        "text": "Rumour.",
        "start": 147.43,
        "duration": 1.42
    },
    {
        "text": "\"o-u-r\".",
        "start": 148.85,
        "duration": 1.41
    },
    {
        "text": "We love our ou's in British English.",
        "start": 150.26,
        "duration": 3.09
    },
    {
        "text": "\"This shouldn't be passed around but...\"",
        "start": 153.35,
        "duration": 4.59
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 157.94,
        "duration": 1.36
    },
    {
        "text": "We're not passing a bucket around; we're not\npassing a charity hat around - we don't want",
        "start": 159.3,
        "duration": 4.73
    },
    {
        "text": "the secret to go any further.",
        "start": 164.03,
        "duration": 2.24
    },
    {
        "text": "\"This shouldn't be passed around but Lionel...\"\ndah-dah-dah-dah-dah.",
        "start": 166.27,
        "duration": 6.23
    },
    {
        "text": "\"This isn't common knowledge but...\"",
        "start": 172.5,
        "duration": 7.94
    },
    {
        "text": "You'll notice with a few of these that we\nare using abbreviations.",
        "start": 180.44,
        "duration": 3.12
    },
    {
        "text": "Now, abbreviations are fine in conversational\nEnglish; just make sure that if you are doing",
        "start": 183.56,
        "duration": 6.47
    },
    {
        "text": "an IELTS writing paper that you're writing\nin full English, so you'd be saying: \"This",
        "start": 190.03,
        "duration": 5.48
    },
    {
        "text": "is not... this should not...\"",
        "start": 195.51,
        "duration": 1.68
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 197.19,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "It's something that would impress an examiner.",
        "start": 198.19,
        "duration": 2.07
    },
    {
        "text": "\"This isn't common knowledge but...\"",
        "start": 200.26,
        "duration": 3.58
    },
    {
        "text": "So, \"common knowledge\" would be what everybody\nknows.",
        "start": 203.84,
        "duration": 5.52
    },
    {
        "text": "So, not everybody knows this.",
        "start": 209.36,
        "duration": 3.25
    },
    {
        "text": "\"Maybe I shouldn't say this but...\"",
        "start": 212.61,
        "duration": 4.89
    },
    {
        "text": "So, I-the person saying the secret-knows that\nit is bad to say this, but then they say it",
        "start": 217.5,
        "duration": 7.86
    },
    {
        "text": "anyway.",
        "start": 225.36,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "So there's an enjoyment of: \"Oo, we're doing\nsomething naughty, but...\"",
        "start": 226.36,
        "duration": 6.18
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay.",
        "start": 232.54,
        "duration": 1.56
    },
    {
        "text": "Another way of drawing the other person into\na conversation - so you say their name, for",
        "start": 234.1,
        "duration": 6.74
    },
    {
        "text": "example: \"Pedro...\" and then they listen to\nme.",
        "start": 240.84,
        "duration": 4.84
    },
    {
        "text": "\"...you know\", and then whoever my rumour\nis about: \"Pedro, you know that Lionel...",
        "start": 245.68,
        "duration": 5.889
    },
    {
        "text": "well, you know Lionel.",
        "start": 251.569,
        "duration": 2.791
    },
    {
        "text": "Well, he did this.",
        "start": 254.36,
        "duration": 2.93
    },
    {
        "text": "He said this.\"",
        "start": 257.29,
        "duration": 1.55
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 258.84,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "So, say the name of the person I'm speaking\nto, and then I share the information.",
        "start": 259.84,
        "duration": 6.669
    },
    {
        "text": "At the end, you don't particularly want to\nget in trouble by that person then sharing",
        "start": 266.509,
        "duration": 8.84
    },
    {
        "text": "this news with everybody, so you're getting\nthem just to keep it to themselves.",
        "start": 275.349,
        "duration": 5.431
    },
    {
        "text": "\"Do you swear you won't tell anyone else?",
        "start": 280.78,
        "duration": 4.509
    },
    {
        "text": "Do you swear?",
        "start": 285.289,
        "duration": 1.65
    },
    {
        "text": "Do you promise you won't tell anyone else?\"",
        "start": 286.939,
        "duration": 6.021
    },
    {
        "text": "Tell anyone else, okay?",
        "start": 292.96,
        "duration": 2.549
    },
    {
        "text": "So, what I'm doing there, is I'm getting that\nperson - the secret ends here.",
        "start": 295.509,
        "duration": 5.93
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay, let's have a go at you guys using these\nyourself.",
        "start": 301.439,
        "duration": 5.191
    },
    {
        "text": "So, I want you to think of something that\nmight have happened at work, or if you're",
        "start": 306.63,
        "duration": 7.23
    },
    {
        "text": "at college, okay?",
        "start": 313.86,
        "duration": 1.399
    },
    {
        "text": "And you're going to practice talking to someone\nelse about something that has happened.",
        "start": 315.259,
        "duration": 5.701
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 320.96,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "So, try to think of something that's happened\nand you're going to share a secret to one",
        "start": 321.96,
        "duration": 4.67
    },
    {
        "text": "of your friends.",
        "start": 326.63,
        "duration": 1.36
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay.",
        "start": 327.99,
        "duration": 1.109
    },
    {
        "text": "\"I've heard...\"",
        "start": 329.099,
        "duration": 2.22
    },
    {
        "text": "Practice that now.",
        "start": 331.319,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "\"I've heard...\" and you'll complete your sentence.",
        "start": 332.319,
        "duration": 3.551
    },
    {
        "text": "Very good.",
        "start": 335.87,
        "duration": 2.799
    },
    {
        "text": "\"Have you heard...?\" using it as a question.",
        "start": 338.669,
        "duration": 3.58
    },
    {
        "text": "Give it a go.",
        "start": 342.249,
        "duration": 1.551
    },
    {
        "text": "\"Have you heard that...?\"",
        "start": 343.8,
        "duration": 4.33
    },
    {
        "text": "Well done.",
        "start": 348.13,
        "duration": 1.349
    },
    {
        "text": "\"They say...\"",
        "start": 349.479,
        "duration": 2.581
    },
    {
        "text": "Give this one a go.",
        "start": 352.06,
        "duration": 1.55
    },
    {
        "text": "\"They say... they say that...\"",
        "start": 353.61,
        "duration": 4.72
    },
    {
        "text": "\"Just between you and me...\"",
        "start": 358.33,
        "duration": 5.35
    },
    {
        "text": "Give that one a go.",
        "start": 363.68,
        "duration": 1.039
    },
    {
        "text": "\"Just between you and me...\"",
        "start": 364.719,
        "duration": 2.331
    },
    {
        "text": "Hope you got that one right.",
        "start": 367.05,
        "duration": 4.209
    },
    {
        "text": "\"I heard on the grapevine that...\"",
        "start": 371.259,
        "duration": 3.491
    },
    {
        "text": "Give that one a go; about your situation at\nwork or at college.",
        "start": 374.75,
        "duration": 6.059
    },
    {
        "text": "\"I heard on the grapevine that...\"",
        "start": 380.809,
        "duration": 3.631
    },
    {
        "text": "\"This shouldn't be passed around but... this\nshouldn't be passed around but...\"",
        "start": 384.44,
        "duration": 10.569
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay, next one: \"This isn't common knowledge\nbut... this isn't common knowledge but...\"",
        "start": 395.009,
        "duration": 9.351
    },
    {
        "text": "\"Maybe I shouldn't say this but...\"",
        "start": 404.36,
        "duration": 6.799
    },
    {
        "text": "Give it a go.",
        "start": 411.159,
        "duration": 3.901
    },
    {
        "text": "And then come up with another of your friend's\nnames and imagine that you're talking to them,",
        "start": 415.06,
        "duration": 9.059
    },
    {
        "text": "then put what your rumour is in here.",
        "start": 424.119,
        "duration": 3.61
    },
    {
        "text": "You put your name of the person you're telling\nthe rumour about here, and then you put the",
        "start": 427.729,
        "duration": 3.46
    },
    {
        "text": "rumour itself here.",
        "start": 431.189,
        "duration": 3.901
    },
    {
        "text": "And then get them to swear to secrecy.",
        "start": 435.09,
        "duration": 2.669
    },
    {
        "text": "Hand on heart - I promise to keep a secret.",
        "start": 437.759,
        "duration": 4.09
    },
    {
        "text": "Thank you for watching today's lesson on rumours\nand secrets.",
        "start": 441.849,
        "duration": 5.671
    },
    {
        "text": "Let's make... not make up any secrets or stories\nabout other people, but let's keep expanding",
        "start": 447.52,
        "duration": 5.06
    },
    {
        "text": "our English and keep the focus.",
        "start": 452.58,
        "duration": 1.57
    },
    {
        "text": "Well done.",
        "start": 454.15,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "See ya next time.",
        "start": 455.15,
        "duration": 0.69
    }
]